[10:11] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'area we would like to adjust. So for example, if&nbsp; I would like to split the top and bottom part,&nbsp;&nbsp; we can do this easily, you know, by selecting&nbsp; both and then drawing the cut line that we did&nbsp;&nbsp; here with the cut tool. And then we can just&nbsp; confirm this. And you can see it\'s quite easy.&nbsp;&nbsp;'

[10:26] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'So we have this then split as well. And you can&nbsp; then basically like this make your separations&nbsp;&nbsp; work and adjust your mask accordingly how&nbsp; you would like to have it in the end. So&nbsp;&nbsp; you can click first confirm to then confirm&nbsp; your mask selection. And once you\'re happy,&nbsp;&nbsp;'

[10:40] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
